  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK134">
<l>maṟappiṉu mōttuk koḷalākum pārppāṉ</l>
<l>piṟappoḻukkaṅ kuṉṟak keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though he forget his reading, he may yet recover it—but if the Brahmin's</l>
<l>conduct decline, his high birth is lost.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
